column1: #List of 666 genes for which we were able to compute clonal frequency
#All driver genes stated as major or those with an FDR < 0.1
##Mean VAF = average variant allele frequency of somatic mutations detected in the driver gene across samples of each tumor type.
##Zvalue = Zscore of the gene's average variant allele frequency in the context of all somatic mutations detected in the tumor type.
##Nmutations = Number of mutations observed in the driver across the cohort
##Pvalue = P-value resulting from the statistical test of major drivers
##MeanCCF = Mean CCF of all mutations detected in drivers of the tumor type
